---
title: Lemongrass Protein Shreds Coconut Curry with Veggies and Pan-Fried Naan
description: There are some flavour combinations that are classics for good reason – lemongrass and coconut milk is one of them! Carrots further enhance the sweetness from these flavour-makers and zesty lime rice brings all the taste elements together! Warm naan seals the deal.
